                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The <b>PRINCE2 Foundation course online</b> is the first of the two PRINCE2 courses, thoughtfully designed to help you get started on your journey as a Project Manager. You will be equipped with the knowledge and expertise to:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
