                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="prince2-foundation-exam-3">
                            <h3>PRINCE2 Foundation Exam</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-3">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-1">1. What is the PRINCE2 Foundation exam pattern and passing score?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Duration: 60 minutes (1 hour)&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Questions: 60 Multiple choice questions&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Pass mark: 33 out of 60 available, or 55%&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Use of textbook: No</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-2">2. Who conducts the exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The exam is conducted through PeopleCert®. KnowledgeHut is an ATO of PeopleCert®.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-3">3. Can I take the PRINCE2 Foundation exam online?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:16.5pt;"><span style="mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;">Yes, you can take the PRINCE2 Foundation exam online through PeopleCert®. You can schedule the exam in advance, at a time and date that suits you. Your exam will be invigilated by a proctor. </span>Make sure that you meet the required&nbsp;<a href="https://www.peoplecert.org/-/media/Resources/Documents/PeopleCert/PASSPORT-Releases/ECSWI268ver020-Online-Proctored-Exams-Candidate-GuidelinesWindows.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span style="mso-bidi-font-size:11pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#26d400;">technical requirements</span></a><span style="mso-bidi-font-size:11pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#444;">&nbsp;</span>to continue with the exam without any issues.<span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;">&nbsp;<span style="color:#444;">
                                                        <o:p></o:p>
                                                    </span></span></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-4">4. Do you provide assistance for the PRINCE2 Foundation exam application process?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes. The aspirants can contact us either by phone or chat if they need help with completing the application form. They can also email us on <a href="http://support@oneitech.com" target="_blank">support@oneitech.com</a> for any course-related queries.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-5">5. Will you give me the exam voucher and exam code for the PRINCE2 Foundation exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes! Once you have completed the workshop, send us an email request for issue of exam voucher and code.&nbsp; Our exam team will email details of your exam code and instructions on how to book through PeopleCert®.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-6">6. If I fail, can I apply for re-evaluation?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>There is no re-evaluation for the PRINCE2 Foundation. However, if you fail you can re-attempt the exam after paying the required fees. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-7">7. Can I retake the PRINCE2 Foundation certification test if I fail? How soon?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-7" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>In case you have failed the PRINCE2 Foundation certification exam, you can retake the exam at a cost, which will depend on the country you will be taking the exam from. Taxes may or may not be applicable. Please contact your Workshop Manager for more information.&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>The retake can be taken anytime after your first attempt.&nbsp;<br></li>
                                                <li>If you wish to save on the Retake Exam Fee, you can sign up for PeopleCert’s 'TAKE2'. For this, you will be required to pay a small amount on top of your course fee, and then later, if you do not clear the exam in the first attempt, your second attempt is completely free of cost.&nbsp;<br></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-8">8. Can I retake the PRINCE2 Foundation exam if I score poorly? How soon?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-8" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>If you have already taken the exam and wish to retake to score better then you will have to purchase the exam again.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-9">9. How soon will I know the result of my exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-9" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>After you have submitted the test, you will get your result within 2 business days. The entire process can take around 5 days. If you have taken the exam through PearsonVUE, PeopleCert® will send a confirmation email to you within 7 days with a link to the e-certificate. Once you activate your PeopleCert® account, you will be able to manage the certificate and buy the hard copy.&nbsp;</p>
                                            <p>You can read more about this here:&nbsp; <a href="https://www.peoplecert.org/help-and-support/FAQ#1FE000DE870C4762A29BBD7493749A90" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">PeopleCert®</a>&nbsp;</p>
                                            <div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX8 SCXW152360496" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;user-select:text;-webkit-user-drag:none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;overflow:visible;cursor:text;clear:both;position:relative;direction:ltr;color:#000;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,&quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif;font-size:12px;">
                                                <p class="Paragraph SCXW152360496 BCX8" paraid="1047653896" paraeid="{3d516ced-0edb-4e29-afe6-529b3972d0e4}{165}" style="margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;user-select:text;-webkit-user-drag:none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;overflow-wrap:break-word;vertical-align:baseline;font-kerning:none;background-color:transparent;color:windowtext;"><br></p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-10">10. How many attempts do I have to pass the PRINCE2 Foundation exam? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-10" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You can give the exam as many times as you want as long as you pay for it each time.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-11">11. How much does PRINCE2 Foundation exam cost?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-11" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The PRINCE2 Foundation Exam cost varies according to your location. Visit the <a href="https://www.peoplecert.org/browse-certifications/project-programme-and-portfolio-management/PRINCE2-2/prince2-foundation-6th-edition-2232" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Peoplecert web page</a> to find the cost at your location.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-12">12. Is PRINCE2 Foundation Exam difficult?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-12" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, the PRINCE2 Foundation Exam is difficult, you would need to prepare for two to three weeks to score well in a <b>PRINCE2 Foundation Exam</b>. Comprehensive training by accredited trainers will also help you get a good understanding of the PRINCE2 frameworks and how to apply it to projects.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-13">13. How many hours of study is needed for PRINCE2 Foundation exam preparation?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-13" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p><b>PRINCE2 Foundation</b> Exam needs preparation of a few weeks. If you can spend 2 to 3 hours every day, you could be exam-ready in two weeks. If you can only spend an hour a day it might take three weeks.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-14">14. How to pass the PRINCE2 Foundation Exam with the revision Checklist?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-14" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>While preparing for your PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Exam, plan your revision to avoid missing out on anything major. Do go through this revision checklist that can guide you to successfully complete your PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Certification:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Understanding the exam:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p>&nbsp;It is important that you should comprehend the structure of the PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Certification Exam. The contents of the question sheet and the issues you should be prepared for should be well understood during the examination.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Revising the Processes&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p>The 7 processes associated with PRINCE2 must be properly understood, as this will help you pass the PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Certification Exam. Review each process carefully before you sit for your test&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Revising the Themes&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p>Are you done reviewing the procedures? Well, seven themes of PRINCE2 are equally important for successfully completing PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation certification. You have to examine each subject and understand them.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Summarizing the Method as one&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p>When you try to learn PRINCE2, it could be challenging for you to discover how all the themes and processes go together. But before you sit for the examination, you should learn to link everything in order to best find solutions to each scenario. Prepare yourself with all the PRINCE2 concepts methods such as the way themes and processes support each of the 7 PRINCE2 principles.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="prince2-foundation-workshop-4">
