                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-1-7">7. What are PRINCE2 Foundation Certification eligibility requirements?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-1-7" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>There are no prerequisites to take the PRINCE 2 Foundations Certification exam. However, it is better if you have some prior understanding of Project Management.&nbsp;</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-1-8">8. What are the exam details for the PRINCE2 Foundation Exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-1-8" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Get sufficient knowledge and understanding of the PRINCE2 method in order to work with or as a member of a project management team running within a PRINCE2 supporting environment by clearing the online PRINCE2 Foundation Exam. This one-hour-long exam has 60 multiple-choice questions out of which you need to score 35 or more to pass the exam.&nbsp;</p>
                                            <p>This online Prince2 Foundation certification confirms that you understand the PRINCE2&nbsp; method and how its elements work. There are three types of questions for the PRINCE2 Foundation Exam: Classic, List, and Missing word.&nbsp;</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-1-9">9. What is the PRINCE2 Foundation Exam Format?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-1-9" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Below mentioned is the exam format for PRINCE2 Foundation Certification Exam:&nbsp;</p>
