            "name": "Can I take the PRINCE2 Foundation exam online?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:16.5pt\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">Yes, you can\r\ntake the PRINCE2 Foundation exam online through PeopleCert®. You can\r\nschedule the exam in advance, at a time and date that suits you. Your exam will\r\nbe invigilated by a proctor. </span>Make sure that you meet the required&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.peoplecert.org/-/media/Resources/Documents/PeopleCert/PASSPORT-Releases/ECSWI268ver020-Online-Proctored-Exams-Candidate-GuidelinesWindows.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#26D400\">technical requirements</span></a><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#444444\">&nbsp;</span>to continue with the exam without any\r\nissues.<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Arial\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#444444\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>"
            }
        }, {
