            "name": "Do you provide assistance for the PRINCE2 Foundation exam application process?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes. The aspirants can contact us either by phone or chat if they need help with completing the application form. They can also email us on <a href=\"http://support@oneitech.com\" target=\"_blank\">support@oneitech.com</a> for any course-related queries.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
