        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "If I fail, can I apply for re-evaluation?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>There is no re-evaluation for the PRINCE2 Foundation. However, if you fail you can re-attempt the exam after paying the required fees. &nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I retake the PRINCE2 Foundation certification test if I fail? How soon?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<ul><li>In case you have failed the PRINCE2 Foundation certification exam, you can retake the exam at a cost, which will depend on the country you will be taking the exam from. Taxes may or may not be applicable. Please contact your Workshop Manager for more information.&nbsp;</li><li>The retake can be taken anytime after your first attempt.&nbsp;<br></li><li>If you wish to save on the Retake Exam Fee, you can sign up for PeopleCert’s 'TAKE2'. For this, you will be required to pay a small amount on top of your course fee, and then later, if you do not clear the exam in the first attempt, your second attempt is completely free of cost.&nbsp;<br></li></ul>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I retake the PRINCE2 Foundation exam if I score poorly? How soon?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>If you have already taken the exam and wish to retake to score better then you will have to purchase the exam again.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How soon will I know the result of my exam?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>After you have submitted the test, you will get your result within 2 business days. The entire process can take around 5 days. If you have taken the exam through PearsonVUE, PeopleCert® will send a confirmation email to you within 7 days with a link to the e-certificate. Once you activate your PeopleCert® account, you will be able to manage the certificate and buy the hard copy.&nbsp;</p><p>You can read more about this here:&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.peoplecert.org/help-and-support/FAQ#1FE000DE870C4762A29BBD7493749A90\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">PeopleCert®</a>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr  BCX8 SCXW152360496\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW152360496 BCX8\" paraid=\"1047653896\" paraeid=\"{3d516ced-0edb-4e29-afe6-529b3972d0e4}{165}\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext;\"><br></p></div>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How many attempts do I have to pass the PRINCE2 Foundation exam? ",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
