                "text": "<p>Our PRINCE2 trainers are: &nbsp;</p><ul><li>Experienced project management professionals  &nbsp;</li><li>Experts who have immense experience in leading, applying, coaching, and teaching about project management&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Our dedicated team of coaches deliver training on par with the standard of excellence as set out by AXELOS. Every candidate receives the same high-quality content irrespective of the trainer and the location. They help you further develop the competencies and skills you need to make a difference in your organization.</p>"
