            "name": "How do I use the revision checklist to pass the PRINCE2 Foundation Exam?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Always revise to avoid missing out on any important topic for your PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Exam.&nbsp;</p><p>Use this revision checklist as a guide to clear your PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Certification&nbsp;</p><ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"●\" data-font=\"Times New Roman\" data-listid=\"48\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Understanding the exam:</strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul><p>You should understand the structure of the PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Certification Exam and get a good grip on the content of the question paper and the types of&nbsp;questions for the exam&nbsp;</p><ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"●\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"32\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Review the Processes</strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul><p>Be clear about the 7 key processes involved in PRINCE2 to pass the PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Certification Exam. Ensure&nbsp;that you&nbsp;have each of the processes thoroughly revised before sitting for your&nbsp;exam&nbsp;</p><ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"●\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"25\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Revise the Themes</strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul><p>Are you done revising the 7 processes? There are 7 themes of PRINCE2 which are equally important for successfully completing PRINCE2. 6th edition Foundation Certification. You need to be thorough and clear with each of these themes.&nbsp;</p><ul>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"●\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"4\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Revising the Method as a whole</strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p>It might be difficult to figure out how everything fits all the topics together. But before you take the examination, make it clear about how they are interconnected, as the issues will underline the same. Stay&nbsp;up-to-date&nbsp;on all concepts and methods concerning PRINCE2, including how each of its 7 PRINCE2 principles supports topics and procedures.&nbsp;</p>"
