                "text": "<p>You surely are aware of the terms ‘Exam Code’ and ‘Exam Voucher’ for applying for the PRINCE2 Foundation Certification Exam. How different are these terms from each other? Here they are:&nbsp;</p><table class=\"table table-bordered\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Differences</b></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Exam Code&nbsp;</b></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Exam Voucher&nbsp;</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Issue</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Issued by PRINCE2. You receive it by email within 24-hours of purchasing your e-learning license.</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Issued once you redeem your exam code.&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Validity</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Its validity lasts for the time your e-learning license lasts&nbsp;</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">The exam voucher is valid for only 1 month&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Use</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">You need your exam code to redeem your exam voucher</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">You need your exam voucher to book your exam</td></tr></tbody></table>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How do I study for PRINCE2 Foundation Exam?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The online PRINCE2 Foundation course will cover all the important topics that you need to prepare for to clear the exam. You need to consistently prepare for the exam spending a few hours every day for few weeks. Use mock tests and other assessments to get yourself exam-ready.<br></p>"
            }
        }]
